<h1 class="font-bold text-2xl text-center">Terms and conditions of partnership and contracting with Emdad platform Company</h1>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2">Preamble</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    Emdad platform is a technical electronic platform designed to facilitate the process between the service applicant and the service provider, to facilitate their process and provide better and faster services, by registering on the platform according to the terms and conditions that shall be mentioned later. The platform's work is summarized by submitting the request by the service applicant through the platform after writing the request information. Accordingly, one or several quotations
    shall be received from service providers. Upon receiving quotation from service providers, the applicant shall choose the service provider based on its desires in terms of price, quality, or otherwise. After the selection and approval of the appropriate service provider through the platform, the service provider shall supply, as agreed upon in the purchase order. The available payment shall be either on credit, prepaid or pay on receipt by using credit cards (Mada - Visa - Apple Pay) or
    direct bank transfer. Financial payments to the service provider shall be in the bank account of the technical supply platform company. After confirming the information, the supply and receipt process, it is transferred to the service provider directly. The service applicant and the service provider shall acknowledge that the technical supply platform company is only an intermediary to provide a direct communication service between the service applicant and the service provider for
    facilitating, speeding up and safety of supply chain process. Your success is our success.
</p>

<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    The following terms and expressions, wherever mentioned in this Agreement, shall have the meanings set forth for each of them, unless the context requires otherwise.
</p>

<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Emdad platform:</strong> the largest electronic platform built with high experience to serve the seller and buyer in the procurement, sale, supply and storage process, with the lowest costs and the best technical and logistical standards.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Application, site or platform:</strong> a database or software process has been fully programmed by Emdad platform with the best technical quality standards allowing its users to deal with (experience - speed - ease - security).
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Additional application:</strong> It is an application serves the platform (Emdad Tools) to be downloaded on mobile devices or smart devices to benefit from shipment tracking services or electronic approval, which is a free service for users of the platform. The same information and login data shall be used for the platform.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Service requester (buyer):</strong> Registration on the platform for making use of the platform services to make requests, track shipments and receive requests.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Service Provider (Seller):</strong> Registration on the platform for making use of the platform services to make quotations, schedule shipments, supply and delivery, and provide distinguished service.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>The first party:</strong> Emdad Platform Company
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>The second party:</strong> The applicant or the service provider
</p>
